      <title>刚果法院随着战争迫在眉睫的战略矿产的统一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/congo-courts-trump-for-strategic-minerals-tie-up-as-war-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果民主共和国为美国独家提供关键矿产和基础设施项目，以换取安全援助，因为它与邻国卢旺达支持的叛乱作斗争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/congo-courts-trump-for-strategic-minerals-tie-up-as-war-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 18:31:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人邀请被解雇的公园护林员，兽医参加特朗普演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/democrats-don-pink-grasp-for-ways-to-rebut-trump-capitol-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乳腺癌幸存者杰西卡·马丁内斯（Jessica Martinez）居住多发性硬化症，依靠医疗补助来支付药物费用，当唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周二晚上向国会发表讲话时，将坐在房屋画廊中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/democrats-don-pink-grasp-for-ways-to-rebut-trump-capitol-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 18:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对美国军事援助的停顿意味着乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/what-trump-s-pause-on-us-military-aid-means-for-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）长期表示，他将迅速结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争。为了达成协议，美国与克里姆林宫互动，同时向基辅施压以支持和平倡议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/what-trump-s-pause-on-us-military-aid-means-for-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 18:13:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国将建立5000亿欧元的国防和基础设施基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/germany-will-set-up-500-billion-special-defense-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据列弗里德里希·梅尔兹（Friedrich Merz）称，德国将建立5000亿欧元（5280亿美元）的基金，作为一项全面的政策大修的一部分，以解决迫切需要在国防和基础设施上进行投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/germany-will-set-up-500-billion-special-defense-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 18:11:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>CFPB因涉嫌对Zelle的欺诈而对美国银行提起诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/cfpb-drops-lawsuit-against-us-banks-over-alleged-fraud-on-zelle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[消费者金融保护局驳回了另一项拜登时代的诉讼，该诉讼针对世界上一些最大的银行，原因是据称急于取出点对点支付网络，然后允许欺诈行为扩散。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/cfpb-drops-lawsuit-against-us-banks-over-alleged-fraud-on-zelle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 18:10:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多说，特朗普在贸易战中的目标是吞并加拿大。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-goal-in-trade-war-is-to-annex-canada-trudeau-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多（Justin Trudeau）在一次激烈的新闻发布会上说，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的目标是摧毁加拿大的经济，以便他可以吞并该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-goal-in-trade-war-is-to-annex-canada-trudeau-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 17:54:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院对墨西哥针对枪手的诉讼表示怀疑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/supreme-court-casts-doubt-on-mexico-s-suit-against-gunmakers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，可能会抛出墨西哥政府诉讼，该诉讼指控包括史密斯（Smith＆amp;韦森·布兰德斯（Wesson Brands Inc.）有助于将枪支向该国的暴力毒品卡特尔（Tublug Cartels）驱动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/supreme-court-casts-doubt-on-mexico-s-suit-against-gunmakers</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 16:38:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽伦斯基（Zelenskiy）在特朗普（Trump）对和平协议（和平协议）之后表示遗憾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/ukraine-s-zelenskiy-says-he-is-ready-to-work-fast-to-end-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）说，他准备迅速努力结束俄罗斯对乌克兰的战争，并强调，他与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在通往和平的道路上的戏剧性陷入困境是“令人遗憾的”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/ukraine-s-zelenskiy-says-he-is-ready-to-work-fast-to-end-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 15:53:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京同意帮助特朗普经纪人与伊朗的核谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/iran-putin-to-help-trump-broker-nuclear-talks-with-tehran</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯同意协助美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）政府与伊朗有关伊斯兰共和国核计划等问题的沟通，并支持其对区域反美国代理人的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/iran-putin-to-help-trump-broker-nuclear-talks-with-tehran</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 11:21:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普升级了全球贸易战，引发了卖山雀的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统施加了他对加拿大和墨西哥的威胁，并以全面的进口征税征收，并对中国的现有指控增加了一倍，这激发了迅速报复，这使世界经济陷入了深入的贸易战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-04/trump-s-canada-mexico-china-tariffs-hit-in-deepening-trade-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Mar 2025 05:01:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
